=== EVENT_STELLAR_NURSERY ===
# id: 55
# title: Stellar Nursery
# chinese_title: 恒星摇篮
# category: Discovery
# mode: starmap

Your scanners detect a region where new stars are forming. The intense radiation is dangerous, but the nascent stellar matter contains rare isotopes worth a fortune.

* [[+30 credits, -5 hull] Mine the protostellar dust]
  ~ gain_credits(30)
  星 (xīng) — star
* [[+20 fuel] Refine stellar hydrogen into fuel]
  ~ gain_fuel(20)
  氢 (qīng) — hydrogen
* [[Gain radical 日] Map the stellar formation patterns]
  ~ gain_radical("日")
  日 (rì) — sun, day
* [[-10 hull, +45 credits] Deep dive into the densest region]
  ~ gain_credits(45)
  深 (shēn) — deep
* [[+5 hull] Use the radiation to recalibrate shields]
  ~ gain_hull(5)
  光 (guāng) — light
